<h2 class='text-center'>Jr. Dev Mentoring's Community of Mentors</h2>
<h4 class='text-center'>How does this work?</h4>
<p class='text-center'>1. Search through the profiles to find someone who you'd be interested in working with.<br> 2. Click on their avatar or name to view their complete profile.<br> 3. If this is someone you would like to work with, click on the <strong>"Click To Connect"</strong> button.<br> 4. An email will be sent to the requested mentor, with instructions on how to connect with you.</p>
